nodes.text: This female doctor was based on the Dathomir Spaceport on the planet Dathomir.

Sometime before 43.5 ABY, when the annual conclave between the Raining Leaves Clan—a clan of Dathomiri Witches—and Broken Columns Clan—a clan made up of men—was to be held, Kaminne Sihn, the leader of the Raining Leaves Clan, went to the Dathomir Spaceport's doctor to seek help regarding her condition. Sihn, like most of her female family members, had a problem bearing a child. The doctor then gave Sihn some medicine to reverse the condition.
